data.description: SELLER OFFERING $2000 TOWARD CLOSING COSTS.....Timeless elegance.. Immaculately clean and well-maintained home! Durability of hardwood floors adorn the majority of the home including 6 fireplaces. Presenting 5 spacious bedrooms plus 2 full baths, the master bedroom offers a walk-in closet with en suite. Dual zoned a/c with 2 separate units. The 2 bedrooms located in the finished 3rd floor both adorned with reading nooks and hardwood floors... as well as all newer windows throughout this absolutely stunning home! The manicured lawn and fully fenced backyard offer a courtyard feel which leads to the detached 2-car garage includes a water spigot, new a/c, electric garage door opener, water & gas line inside the garage as well as a drain in the floor for easy drainage. Only a short distance to the City Park. PHS school district. Close to shopping, restaurants, and public transportation. This home is a must see!! ...ACCEPTING FHA, VA, CONVENTIONAL FINANCING AS WELL AS CASH.
